			subtitle: "The Mind Stone is a essencially a limitless Storage for XP. It can be activated using the 'Change Mode' key. Once activated, it will rapidely suck all of your XP levels. The XP levels can be retrived by Right Clicking with the Stone. When it's placed on a Dark Matter Pedestal, it will suck all the nearby XP orbs"
