			subtitle: "The Life Stone is a combination of the Body Stone and the Soul Stone. It will both heal you and keep your hunger bar filled, as long as you have redstone in your inventory to keep it running. When placed on a Dark Matter Pedestal, it will heal the nearby players and will also keep their hunger bars filled"
