		{
			x: 4.5d
			y: -7.0d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "Advanced Teleporter. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Advanced Dislocator is a major upgrade for your teleportation needs."
				""
				"By Shift Right Clicking with it, you can access its configuration panel. Here you can set multiple locations, based off of your current one. You can also add Ender Pearls as fuel. Without Fuel, the Dislocator, won't work. "
				""
				"After you've selected a location, just close the GUI, and Right Click the Dislocator to teleport to that selected location. This action will consume one Fuel."
				""
				"The Dislocator also has a Blink mode which will basically turn you into an Enderman. You'll be able to teleport forwand on a short range with this mode."
			]
			dependencies: ["2EDEE17460BCCE94"]
