			subtitle: "As if things weren't interesting enough. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"Any Mob Farm created at this stage would require a worthy Mob Grinder. That's where this puppy comes in."
				""
				"The Draconic Mob Grinder will kill all the mobs present in a 7x7 area in front of it."
				""
				"It is recommanded that you use an XP Hopper to collect all the XP produced."
				""
				"Lastly, the Mob grinder can be powered either externally, or with a Capacitor in the power slot of the Grinder GUI."
			]
			dependencies: ["212CBE2DA076A4E3"]
