		{
			x: 3.0d
			y: -30.0d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "The Hydroponic Bed is a machine designed to boost the spedd growth of crops. It will use water (and lava for nether crops) to boost the growing speed of crops. If Ether Gas is used, the crops will be boosted even more. They'll also be harvested automatically. The Crop has to be planted directly on the Hydroponic Bed. Ether Gas can be obtained in an Alchemical Imbuer with some Industrial Foregoing Fertilizer and some Liquid Hydrongen Chloride"
