			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "The Plant Gatherer is a machine designed to harvest trees and crops. If a tree is bigger then the working area of the Gatherer, the tree will still be harvested entirely. The Gatherer will also produce small amounts of Sludge for each operation. Sludge can later be refined into new items"
